Debbie Ugochukwu Collins nuru (amụrụ n'abalị iri na ise n"ọnwa Anọ, n'afọ otu puku, nari iteolu na iri iteolu na abụọ (15 Eprel 1992) onye Nlereanya na ịma mma nke Naijiria ji njide aha  na onye na-eme ihe ngosi mara mma nke nọchitere anya Naijiria na asọmpi Miss World 2016.listen (help·info) Ọ pụtakwara onye mbụ gbara ọsọ na mbipụta 2015 nke Best Girl in Nigeria pageant wee nweta ya ohere ịnọchite anya Naijiria na Miss Universe 2015

N'abalị iri abụọ na anọ n'ọnwa iri n'afọ puku abụo na iri na ise (24Ọktoba n"afọ 2015), a họpụtara Debbie dị ka onye nke abụọ n "Nwa agbọghọ kachasị mma na Naịjirịa n'"afọ puku abụọ na iri na ise (2015) mgbe ọ na-anọchite anya Ebonyi Steeti
Ọ nọchitere anya Naijiria na asọmpi Miss Universe 2015 na US.
Debbie nọchitere anya Naijiria na Miss World 2016
Nwa agbọghọ kacha mma na Naịjirịa asọmpi emeghị na 2016 ma dị ka onye mbụ na-esote na afọ puku abụọ na iri na ise (2015) gara aga, a họpụtara ya ka ọ nọchite anya Nigeria na Miss World 2016 pageant.
